{
  "id": "api/core/TypeDecorator",
  "title": "TypeDecorator",
  "contents": "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"typedecorator\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TypeDecorator#typedecorator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>TypeDecorator</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th>npm Package</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\">@angular/core</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th>Module</th>\n  <td><code>import { TypeDecorator } from <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th>Source</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/4.3.0-rc.0/packages/core/src/util/decorators.ts#L44-L89\">core/src/util/decorators.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<h2 id=\"interface-overview\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TypeDecorator#interface-overview\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>Interface Overview</h2>\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface TypeDecorator { \n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/TypeDecorator#call\">&#x3C;T extends Type&#x3C;any>>(type: T): T</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/TypeDecorator#annotations\">annotations: any[]</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/TypeDecorator#Class\">Class(obj: ClassDefinition): Type&#x3C;any></a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TypeDecorator#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>Description</h2>\n  <p>An interface implemented by all Angular type decorators, which allows them to be used as ES7\ndecorators as well as\nAngular DSL syntax.</p>\n<p>DSL syntax:</p>\n<code-example>\nvar MyClass = ng\n  .Component({...})\n  .Class({...});\n</code-example>\n<p>ES7 syntax:</p>\n<code-example>\n@ng.Component({...})\nclass MyClass {...}\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-members\">\n  <h2 id=\"members\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TypeDecorator#members\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>Members</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"call\"></a>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">&#x3C;T extends Type&#x3C;any>>(type: T): T</code-example>\n  <p>Invoke as ES7 decorator.</p>\n\n  </div>\n\n    \n    <details class=\"overloads\">\n      <summary>Overloads</summary>\n      <div class=\"detail-contents\">\n        \n        <div class=\"instance-member-overload\">\n  <a id=\"call(target:%20Object,%20propertyKey?:%20string%7Csymbol,%20parameterIndex?:%20number)\"></a>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">(target: Object, propertyKey?: string|symbol, parameterIndex?: number): void</code-example>\n  \n  </div>\n\n        \n        \n      </div>\n    </details>\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"annotations\"></a>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">annotations: any[]</code-example>\n  <p>Storage for the accumulated annotations so far used by the DSL syntax.</p>\n<p>Used by <a href=\"api/core/Class\"><code><a href=\"api/core/Class\">Class</a></code></a> to annotate the generated class.</p>\n\n  </div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"Class\"></a>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">Class(obj: ClassDefinition): Type&#x3C;any></code-example>\n  <p>Generate a class from the definition and annotate it with <a href=\"api/core/TypeDecorator#annotations\"><code><a href=\"api/core/TypeDecorator\">TypeDecorator</a></code></a>.</p>\n\n  </div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>"
}